title: Episode 17 w/ Havoc (of Mobb Deep)
itunes:title: Episode 17 w/ Havoc (of Mobb Deep)
description:
N.O.R.E. and DJ EFN are the Drink Champs. In this episode the guys drink it up with Havoc of the legendary Queensbridge duo; Mobb Deep. They talk about past misunderstandings between Mobb Deep and CNN, a possible Queens tour, Prince, working with Kanye West and more. --- Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/drinkchamps/support
